item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - Madonna - Holiday -- Madonna (2001 Remaster)
item.description:
Does anyone have the full version of Holiday from the 2001 remaster of Madonna's debut self-titled album in FLAC?

Digital versions of this album have The Immaculate Collection version of Holiday which is actually an error on the publishers part.

Tidal, Qobuz and most others only have the version I mentioned.
item.author: lordemisrule
